JD 14:

Objectives and Responsibilities of the Role
The person will work alongside the core team at BrandLoom to help deliver the overall eCommerce solutions to the clients while playing a key role in driving the online marketplace business.

Responsible for managing & growing the eCommerce marketplace business.
Open up new third party eCommerce platforms for clients by listing relevant categories & products.
Build on the existing business by adding new categories and product portfolio listings on the marketplaces.
Work closely with the clients eCommerce team to build the brand on e-comm platforms.
Undertake digital marketing – organic and paid media initiatives to drive performance & channel sales.
Product Portfolio management – Assist the team with product sales and category performance inputs to optimize the product portfolio from time to time.
Oversee the day-to-day marketplace eCommerce operations, customer service, updates, post listings, promotions, merchandising, maintenance and performance.
Stay up-to-date with the promotional calendars and plans of eCommerce platforms. Drive category interventions.
Gather intelligence from eCommerce platforms to further strengthen the brand’s offering.

